data.description: Waterfront entertainers' paradise! Relax in a lovely sunroom while enjoying breathtaking views of Lake Ponchartrain. Boathouse complete w/ lift & dock and direct access to lake. Fish, crab, swim, and kayak from your private deck. Spacious party area includes screened patio. Primary bedroom on first level and two spacious bedrooms on upper level. Flex space downstairs is ideal for additional living, bedroom or office. Easy access to New Orleans & Mississippi makes a great primary residence or weekend getaway
